description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for VLAN-tagged network traffic over an Elastic Network Interface (ENI). This feature is in limited Preview for this release. Contact your account manager if you are interested in this feature.
[``botocore``] This release enables fast cloning in Aurora Serverless. You can now clone between Aurora Serverless clusters and Aurora Provisioned clusters.
[``botocore``] Adds AWS Secrets Manager Access Token Authentication for Source Locations
